    "For proofreading, CAVE builds on the ChunkedGraph 28, 29.",
    "Like previous systems 26, 30, 31, the ChunkedGraph represents cells as connected components in a supervoxel (groups of voxels) graph.",
    "It is currently the only system for neuron-based proofreading by a distributed community but was too costly to be used on petascale datasets.",
    "Here, as one part of CAVE, we introduce the next generation of this system, the ChunkedGraph v2, which scales proofreading to petascale datasets through a more cost-efficient storage implementation.",
